            <article class="a-main  " data-article-url="https://www.wired.co.uk/article/thomas-piketty-capital-ideology" data-article-type="article" data-article-uid="31e5oenB2Gl" data-meta-title="This economist has a radical plan to solve wealth inequality | WIRED UK">
